Bear Stearns and Co said it bought aspecialist book yesterday on the American Stock Exchange butwould not disclose the name or the price.    "It deals in stocks and options and it just demonstratesour faith in the auction system on the exchange," said AlvinEinbender, chief executive officer of Bear Stearns. "It'sevidence of the fact we have an appetite for that sort of thingand think there's a good future in the marketplace," he said. Reuter&#3;